Output ../.vhs/intro.mp4

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 12
Set Width 638
Set Height 430
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 15
Set TypingSpeed 80ms

Hide
Type "cd ~/Developer/Sandbox/demo-vaultry 2>/dev/null || cd /tmp && export PS1='$ ' && clear && figlet -f slant 'claude-secrets' | lolcat -f -F 0.2"
Enter
Sleep 300ms
Show

Sleep 2000ms

Type "claude"
Sleep 800ms
Enter
Sleep 1200ms
